statements.sql: with recursive `laravel_cte` as ((select *, 0 as `depth`, cast(`id` as char(65535)) as `path`, cast(`name` as char(65535)) as `name_path`, cast(`slug` as char(65535)) as `slug_path` from `categories` where `parent_id` is null) union all (select `categories`.*, `depth` + 1 as `depth`, concat(`path`, '.', `categories`.`id`), concat(`name_path`, '/', `categories`.`name`), concat(`slug_path`, '/', `categories`.`slug`) from `categories` inner join `laravel_cte` on `laravel_cte`.`id` = `categories`.`parent_id`)) select * from `laravel_cte` where `slug` = 'prof-stephan-wehner' limit 1
